{"name":"Simple Energy","permalink":"simple-energy","crunchbase_url":"http://www.crunchbase.com/company/simple-energy","homepage_url":"http://simpleenergy.com","blog_url":"http://utilities.simpleenergy.com/blog","blog_feed_url":"http://utilities.simpleenergy.com/blog/feed","twitter_username":"simpleenergy","category_code":"software","number_of_employees":14,"founded_year":2011,"founded_month":1,"founded_day":24,"deadpooled_year":null,"deadpooled_month":null,"deadpooled_day":null,"deadpooled_url":null,"tag_list":"cleantech, energy, energy-efficiency, green, web-2-0, facebook, social-networking","alias_list":null,"email_address":"info@simpleenergy.com","phone_number":"","description":"Changing how people save energy","created_at":"Fri Dec 17 22:13:14 UTC 2010","updated_at":"Sat Oct 27 04:59:03 UTC 2012","overview":"<p>Simple Energy uses social game mechanics to change how people save energy and how utilities engage customers. They make saving energy &#8220;social, fun and simple.&#8221;</p>\n\n<p>By engaging people on the platforms they already use, including email, Facebook, web, and mobile applications, and making energy use data into a simple scoring system that allows people to compete with their friends and neighbors online, Simple Energy encourages people to become interested in their own energy use and take action to reduce consumption. The system is based on leading behavioral economics and game mechanics research by scientific advisor Dan Ariely, author of Predictably Irrational and The Upside of Irrationality. Results from a recent pilot program show that the platform can produce an average energy savings of 20% with up to 50% in savings for top performers.</p>","image":{"available_sizes":[[[150,29],"assets/images/resized/0014/7146/147146v2-max-150x150.png"],[[250,48],"assets/images/resized/0014/7146/147146v2-max-250x250.png"],[[450,87],"assets/images/resized/0014/7146/147146v2-max-450x450.png"]],"attribution":null},"products":[],"relationships":[{"is_past":